headline: How DoorDash’s Expansion and Recent Price Swings Are Shaping Its 2025 Valuation
summary: Wondering if DoorDash is worth buying at today’s prices? You’re not alone, especially with so much buzz about its future growth and profitability. headline: DoorDash (DASH) Stock Is Up, What You Need To Know
summary: Shares of on-demand food delivery service DoorDash (NYSE:DASH) jumped 4.3% in the afternoon session after a director at the company and partner at a major investor, Sequoia Capital, purchased approximately $100 million worth of its shares.

headline: CaringBridge and DoorDash Partner to Double Donations up to $50,000 on Giving Tuesday
summary: Tomorrow, on Giving Tuesday, CaringBridge will kick off a month-long holiday giving campaign. The Giving Tuesday campaign is thanks to gift card partner, DoorDash, the local commerce platform that connects people with their favorite businesses. All donations received on CaringBridge.org on Giving Tuesday will be matched by Door Dash, dollar for dollar, up to $50,000.
